title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update IX Italy & Malta - Rome
description:
In this video we will have a look at Rome which has received a massive update as part of World Update IX. Both the photogrammetry content and the number of POI's have been improved. The POI's do include multiple churches but also the Vatican which is located near Rome.
